text: You like spicy food, right? Let's see how much chili can you eat!
And a glass of chili water!
Wow, spicy chicken! I like it!
Why don't you eat?
It doesn't smell spicy at all! I need to put something really good.
Em, that's the right way!
Are you choked? Come and have a drink.
The water is so sweet!
Sweet? How could it be? Let me taste.
You are a bad guy!
(The first day getting salaries)
(Paycheck arrived 3,000 yuan)
Waiter, the menu, please!
We want to the best and the most expensive dish!
Wait a moment! And two bottle of Lafite wine.
(One week after getting salaries)
What are you doing? It' mine!
No, it belongs to me!
I gonna hide the chili jam inside. Let's see how Ermao could do.
Let me help you, bro!
I need to take the firewood into the kitchen.
(I'm still here...>.<)
Ah! I've been fooled by Songsong!
You are not smart enough, haha!
Finally, I got chili jam!
Ah... It's tomato jam? I was fooled again!
Eating with the girlfriend (Expectation)
Oh baby, you are too tired recently. You should eat more meat.
Baby, the soup is good, come and taste.
Well, not bad!
Eating with the girlfriend (Reality)
This meal is not tasty at all! It's yours!
The meat would make me fat. It's all yours!
What are you doing? I like the soup! So it's all mine!
Do you have the same experience?
When Guizhounese and Shanxinese eat rice noodles.
(Shanxinese)
Em.... The rice noodles are not sour at all!
(Guizhounese)
Em... the rice noodles are not spicy at all.
Give back our money!!
Easy, bro! Do you want to taste our new rice noodles? You will be satisfied this time!
Em.... sour enough. Good!
Em... spicy enough!
We wanna more!
Eating Instant noodle when we were children.
Wow! It smells so good! I wish I could eat instant noodle everyday when I grow up!
You are eating instant noodle! Can I eat some?
Fine, give me your hands.
Eating instant noodle when we grow up
Bro, I don't want to eat instant noodle anymore! It makes me sick of my stomach.
I'll take you to the restaurant after today's work.
(This smell again)
This one is yours, too. I go to work now.
